**Banks Require:**
- Property title
- Building ownership
- Additional assets
- Guarantors with property

## 2026 No Collateral Solution

**Equipment as Security:**
- Equipment acts as collateral
- Hypothecation registered
- Insurance required
- JPJ registration (vehicles)
- **No property needed**

## Real No Collateral Approvals

**Case:** Contractor, rented premises
**Need:** Komatsu PC200
**Collateral:** Equipment only
**Financing:** RM 180,000, 0% down
**Approved:** fasts

