| **Property Risk** | High | Low (equipment only) |
| **Approval Time** | 2-3 weeks | fasts |
| **Interest Rate** | 4.5-5.5% | 5.0-6.0% |
| **Documentation** | Complex | Simple |

## Get No Collateral Equipment

No property but need equipment? Apply for equipment-only financing.

---

**Income focus?** See [No EPF Equipment](/blog/no-epf-equipment-2026-income-based).

    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <CTAButton href="/en/contact">Apply for Equipment Financing</CTAButton>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>